0.title: Full-Stack Developer - Java/Spring Boot/Angular for Enterprise Microservices Architecture
0.description:
We are seeking an expert Full-Stack Developer to join our enterprise-level microservices project. This is a complex, large-scale initiative requiring deep expertise in modern development technologies and enterprise architecture patterns.

**Project Overview:**
You'll be working on building and enhancing scalable microservices architecture for enterprise applications. This is a long-term project (6+ months) that involves designing, developing, and deploying robust, high-performance solutions that can handle enterprise-scale traffic and data processing.

**Required Technical Skills:**
• Java - Expert level proficiency
• Spring Boot - Advanced microservices development
• Angular - Modern frontend development
• MySQL - Database design and optimization
• Docker - Containerization and deployment
• Kubernetes - Container orchestration and management
• Jenkins - CI/CD pipeline development and automation

**What We're Looking For:**
• Proven experience in enterprise-level application development
• Strong background in building scalable microservices architectures
• Deep understanding of distributed systems and cloud-native technologies
• Experience with DevOps practices and automated deployment pipelines
• Ability to work independently and deliver high-quality solutions
• Strong communication skills for collaborative development

**Project Scope:**
This is a large-scale project involving multiple interconnected microservices, complex business logic, and integration with various enterprise systems. You'll be responsible for both backend API development and frontend user interface implementation.

**Contract Details:**
This position offers potential for conversion to full-time employment after successful completion of the initial contract period.

If you have the expertise we're looking for and are passionate about enterprise-scale development, we'd love to hear from you!
